import { AppBar, Button, Tab, Tabs, Tooltip, Typography } from "@mui/material"
function navBar() {
  return (
    <>
      <AppBar>
        <Tooltip sx={{flex:1}}>
            <Typography variant="h6">LOGO</Typography>
            <Tabs>
                <Tab></Tab>
            </Tabs>
            <Button variant="contained">Login</Button>
        </Tooltip>
      </AppBar>
    </>
  )
}

export default navBar
